{"id":27773,"date":"2020-09-05T20:26:59","date_gmt":"2020-09-05T13:26:59","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=27773"},"modified":"2020-10-03T20:56:09","modified_gmt":"2020-10-03T13:56:09","slug":"huong-dan-cai-dat-google-amp-cho-blog-wordpress-mien-phi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/wordpress\/huong-dan-cai-dat-google-amp-cho-blog-wordpress-mien-phi","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t Google AMP cho blog WordPress mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed chi ti\u1ebft t\u1eeb A-Z"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\"><a href=\"https:\/\/amp.dev\/\">Google AMP<\/a> l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea3i trang d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t gi\u00e2y tr\u00ean THI\u1ebeT B\u1eca DI \u0110\u1ed8NG k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi d\u00f9ng hosting gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>R\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u blog \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u1edbi t\u1ed1i \u01b0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea3i trang \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Google v\u00e0 t\u0103ng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng m\u00e0 qu\u00ean m\u1ea5t AMP, m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1ng server cache tr\u00ean m\u00e1y ch\u1ee7 Google gi\u00fap m\u1ecdi trang web lu\u00f4n load d\u01b0\u1edbi 1 gi\u00e2y t\u1eeb trang k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a Google. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Facebook Article Instant.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Google AMP kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 d\u00f9ng c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac ri\u00eang \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i script h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a CSS. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac Schema, AMP lu\u00f4n kh\u1eaft khe trong vi\u1ec7c x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 x\u1ea3y ra l\u1ed7i x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c n\u00e0o th\u00ec xem nh\u01b0 Google s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i cache trang \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t blog chu\u1ea9n AMP kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>T\u0103ng doanh thu t\u1eeb Google Adsense<\/li><li>T\u0103ng th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng SEO<\/li><li>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb9p<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h2>C\u00e1ch Google AMP ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a AMP<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>&#8220;AMP r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 cho website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 lead&#8221;<br>&#8220;AMP l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m thu nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb Google AdSense&#8221;<br>&#8220;AMP g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 cho thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website&#8221;<\/p><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 AMP, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang trong nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, ri\u00eang v\u1edbi blog th\u00ec n\u00f3 s\u1ebd sai, AMP ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u0103ng doanh thu, SEO v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb9p mong mu\u1ed1n. \u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp AMP \u0111\u00fang.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>AMP ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u01b0u cache blog c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u00ean m\u00e1y ch\u1ee7 Google v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 HTML, CSS v\u00e0 JavaScript gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1edf trang b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00ean l\u1eeda.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>AMP s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m si\u00eau m\u01b0\u1ee3t khi xem trang v\u00ec tinh gi\u1ea3n m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf hao t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean m\u00e1y ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u1edd cache tr\u00ean server Google v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 MI\u1ec4N D\u1ecaCH v\u1edbi AdBlocker.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, trong khi AMP r\u00fat g\u1ecdn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u01b0u ti\u00ean hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb m\u1ecdi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o AMP Ads kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang Google Adsense m\u00e0 c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 t\u00f4i n\u00f3i AMP l\u00e0m t\u0103ng doanh thu qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o cho b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1eed huy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Google Adsense l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u1edfi tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t v\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm blog. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi AMP hai \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0y s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf tr\u00ean di \u0111\u1ed9ng. Tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng n\u00e0o!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t Google AMP cho blog WordPress nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Plugin h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t blog AMP l\u00e0 plugin tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed <a href=\"\/out\/ampforwp\" data-eafl-id=\"27752\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">AMPforWP<\/a>, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 tr\u00f9m cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a AMP plugin v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Google AMP.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi plugin \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t blog AMP mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed nh\u1edd v\u00e0o plugin mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a WordPress l\u00e0 AMP plugin.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t theme h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 AMP native (tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ecdn)<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Theme h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 AMP th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1 m\u1eafc so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c theme kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>May m\u1eafn l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 <a href=\"\/out\/astratheme\" data-eafl-id=\"22449\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\">theme Astra mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/a> h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 AMP.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u00f3 blog s\u1eb5n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i sang theme Astra c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00fd ki\u1ebfn hay. C\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 d\u00f9ng giao di\u1ec7n <strong>AMP Reader<\/strong>. N\u00f3 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t theme AMP ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c theme b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 R\u1ea4T HO\u00c0N H\u1ea2O \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u1ed5n c\u1ea3<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>D\u00f9ng theme Astra mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/strong>. T\u00f9y bi\u1ebfn theme AMP s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<\/li><li><strong>D\u00f9ng giao di\u1ec7n AMP reader<\/strong>. S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi theme hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn n\u00e0y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 AMP Reader h\u01a1n b\u1edfi v\u00ec ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 l\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u00f9ng theme g\u00ec.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0 c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh AMP plugin<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>AMP plugin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o b\u1edfi Automattic v\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u00ean b\u1ea3n 2.0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch t\u00e2n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng. \u1ed4n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n <a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/amp\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/amp\/\">download plugin AMP v\u1ec1 trong WordPress Repo<\/a> v\u00e0 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t xong, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch th\u00eam l\u00e0 AMP plugin c\u00f3 3 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Transitional Mode<\/strong>. B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khi b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng theme h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh AMP nh\u01b0 Astra.<\/li><li><strong>Standard Mode<\/strong>. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n khi t\u1ea1o ra 2 URL kh\u00e1c nhau c\u1ee7a c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t trang. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y.<\/li><li><strong>Reader Mode<\/strong>. D\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t theme AMP template kh\u00e1c t\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n theme \u0111ang d\u00f9ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t URL cho c\u1ea3 trang AMP v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng AMP. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00f4i khuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignwide size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1676\" height=\"910\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ba-che-do-amp-plugin.png\" alt=\"Ba Che Do Amp Plugin\" class=\"wp-image-27794\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ba-che-do-amp-plugin.png 1676w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ba-che-do-amp-plugin-218x118.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ba-che-do-amp-plugin-300x163.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ba-che-do-amp-plugin-700x380.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ba-che-do-amp-plugin-768x417.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ba-che-do-amp-plugin-1024x556.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1676px) 100vw, 1676px\" \/><figcaption>3 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 AMP<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"956\" height=\"849\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Lua-chon-AMP-Reader-Theme.png\" alt=\"Lua Chon Amp Reader Theme\" class=\"wp-image-27812\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Lua-chon-AMP-Reader-Theme.png 956w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Lua-chon-AMP-Reader-Theme-218x194.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Lua-chon-AMP-Reader-Theme-300x266.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Lua-chon-AMP-Reader-Theme-700x622.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Lua-chon-AMP-Reader-Theme-768x682.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 956px) 100vw, 956px\" \/><figcaption>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 theme AMP reader \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"426\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2-theme-cung-kich-hoat-trong-giao-dien-theme-1024x426.png\" alt=\"2 Theme Cung Kich Hoat Trong Giao Dien Theme\" class=\"wp-image-27813\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2-theme-cung-kich-hoat-trong-giao-dien-theme-1024x426.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2-theme-cung-kich-hoat-trong-giao-dien-theme-218x91.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2-theme-cung-kich-hoat-trong-giao-dien-theme-300x125.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2-theme-cung-kich-hoat-trong-giao-dien-theme-700x291.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2-theme-cung-kich-hoat-trong-giao-dien-theme-768x320.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2-theme-cung-kich-hoat-trong-giao-dien-theme.png 1343w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 2 theme c\u00f9ng k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t (tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 theme ch\u00ednh, ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 theme AMP)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 Reader Mode, b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam CSS v\u00e0o AMP b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh theme trong Additional CSS c\u1ee7a theme b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t AMP Google Analytics<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Google b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c plugin kh\u00e1c ch\u00e8n tr\u00ean blog s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e8n v\u00e0o AMP b\u1edfi v\u00ec Google AMP d\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t m\u00e3 track kh\u00e1c ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi blog b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u00e3 track c\u1ee7a AMP c\u00f3 d\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;amp-analytics type=\"googleanalytics\">\n  &lt;script type=\"application\/json\">\n  {\n    \"vars\": {\n      \"account\": \"UA-XXXXX-Y\"\n    },\n    \"triggers\": {\n      \"trackPageview\": {\n        \"on\": \"visible\",\n        \"request\": \"pageview\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  &lt;\/script>\n&lt;\/amp-analytics>\n&lt;script async custom-element=\"amp-analytics\"    src=\"https:\/\/cdn.ampproject.org\/v0\/amp-analytics-0.1.js\">&lt;\/script>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i \u1edf ch\u1ed7 l\u00e0 AMP plugin c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ch\u00e8n m\u00e3 Google Analytics \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch d\u00e1n&nbsp;<code>googleanalytics<\/code>&nbsp;v\u00e0o \u00f4 Vendor type.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video controls src=\"https:\/\/media.cuongthach.com\/file\/CuongThach\/Huong-dan-cach-chen-Google-Analytics-AMP.mp4\"><\/video><figcaption>Th\u00eam Google Analytics<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Facebook Pixel l\u00e0&nbsp;<code>facebookpixel<\/code>&nbsp;ho\u1eb7c <code>gtag<\/code> cho Google Tag Manager.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t AMP Google Adsense<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video aligncenter\"><video controls src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/amp-ads.mp4\"><\/video><figcaption>AMP Ads<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng plugin <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/ad-inserter\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/ad-inserter\/\" target=\"_blank\">Ads Insert Plugin<\/a> mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, plugin n\u00e0y li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Google Adsense c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u00e8n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 AMP post.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignwide size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cach-chen-Google-Adsense-AMP.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1869\" height=\"944\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cach-chen-Google-Adsense-AMP.png\" alt=\"Cach Chen Google Adsense Amp\" class=\"wp-image-27805\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cach-chen-Google-Adsense-AMP.png 1869w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cach-chen-Google-Adsense-AMP-218x110.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cach-chen-Google-Adsense-AMP-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cach-chen-Google-Adsense-AMP-700x354.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cach-chen-Google-Adsense-AMP-768x388.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cach-chen-Google-Adsense-AMP-1024x517.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1869px) 100vw, 1869px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>D\u00e1n 1 v\u00e0o &lt;head&gt; tag v\u00e0 2 v\u00e0o &lt;body&gt; tag b\u1eb1ng Ads Insert Plugin<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"836\" height=\"829\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chen-quang-cao-vao-AMP.png\" alt=\"Chen Quang Cao Vao Amp\" class=\"wp-image-27808\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chen-quang-cao-vao-AMP.png 836w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chen-quang-cao-vao-AMP-218x216.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chen-quang-cao-vao-AMP-300x297.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chen-quang-cao-vao-AMP-700x694.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/chen-quang-cao-vao-AMP-768x762.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 836px) 100vw, 836px\" \/><figcaption>Ads Insert Plugin<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t AMP Schema Structure<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"\/out\/seopress\" data-eafl-id=\"22427\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\">SEOPress<\/a> v\u00e0 <a href=\"https:\/\/rankmath.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Rankmath<\/a> t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch 100% v\u1edbi AMP n\u00ean khi b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o schema cho blog th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o lu\u00f4n cho AMP.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng YoastSEO th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0i th\u00eam plugin Schema c\u00f3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 AMP.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ki\u1ec3m tra AMP c\u00f3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1ed5n hay ch\u01b0a<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 test nhanh AMP b\u1eb1ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/search.google.com\/test\/amp\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/search.google.com\/test\/amp\" target=\"_blank\">Google AMP Test<\/a> b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch d\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link <code>https:\/\/domaincuaban.com\/bai-viet-thu\/?amp<\/code> v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed (L\u01b0u \u00fd c\u00f3 <code>?amp<\/code> ph\u00eda sau khi d\u00f9ng AMP Reader Mode). B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ki\u1ec3m tra c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac Schema t\u1ea1i <a href=\"https:\/\/search.google.com\/test\/rich-results\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/search.google.com\/test\/rich-results\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Google Schema Test<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n xem giao di\u1ec7n AMP c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec th\u00eam&nbsp;<code>?amp<\/code>&nbsp;v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i URL c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 trang n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n (\u00e1p d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi AMP readmode), b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y giao di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf d\u1ea1ng AMP.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n Google Search Console b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng &#8220;Inspect Any URL&#8221; hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 fetch as Google \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra c\u00f3 b\u00e1o l\u1ed7i g\u00ec kh\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra ngay trong WordPress Admin, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Plugin AMP s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00e1o l\u1ed7i cho b\u1ea1n. N\u1ebfu plugin b\u00e1o l\u1ed7i th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eeda b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch xem pluin n\u00e0o \u0111ang t\u1ea1o markup l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 t\u1eaft n\u00f3 khi ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 AMP.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignwide size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AMP-bao-loi.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"723\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AMP-bao-loi.png\" alt=\"Amp Bao Loi\" class=\"wp-image-27798\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AMP-bao-loi.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AMP-bao-loi-218x154.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AMP-bao-loi-300x212.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AMP-bao-loi-700x494.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AMP-bao-loi-768x542.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>AMP plugin b\u00e1o l\u1ed7i t\u1ea1i th\u1ebb Validated URLs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1999\" height=\"851\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/amp-plugin-suppression.png\" alt=\"Amp Plugin Suppression\" class=\"wp-image-27792\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/amp-plugin-suppression.png 1999w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/amp-plugin-suppression-218x93.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/amp-plugin-suppression-300x128.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/amp-plugin-suppression-700x298.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/amp-plugin-suppression-768x327.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/amp-plugin-suppression-1024x436.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px\" \/><figcaption>C\u00e1ch s\u1eeda l\u1ed7i: B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n &#8220;Suppressed&#8221; (t\u1eaft \u0111i) plugin n\u00e0o t\u1ea1o l\u1ed7i<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o L\u1ed6I \u0110\u1ece, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng AMP s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Google cache. Xem nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn, xin nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 AMP kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c blog tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp khi c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 t\u0103ng si\u00eau t\u1ed1c t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1edf trang b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u1edf trang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f9a Google (SERP), l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn SEO.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Google \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh g\u1ea7n 5 n\u0103m li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n AMP k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m 2015. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 Google b\u1ecf nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2m huy\u1ebft cho c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"\/mindset\/blogspot-la-gi\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"19030\">Blogspot<\/a> v\u00e0 <a href=\"\/copywriting\/ghost-cms-nen-tang-viet-blog-chuyen-dung-thay-the-wordpress\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"27352\">Ghost CMS<\/a> \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng AMP c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n cho SEO n\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng n\u00ean h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi hai n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng chuy\u00ean blog n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n g\u00ec h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn nh\u00e9<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Google AMP l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea3i trang d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t gi\u00e2y tr\u00ean thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi d\u00f9ng hosting gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":27811,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[42],"tags":[78,58],"featured_image_urls":{"full":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/huong-dan-cai-dat-AMP-cho-blog-WordPress-mien-phi.png",1024,512,false],"thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/huong-dan-cai-dat-AMP-cho-blog-WordPress-mien-phi-300x150.png",270,135,true],"medium":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/huong-dan-cai-dat-AMP-cho-blog-WordPress-mien-phi-700x350.png",700,350,true],"medium_large":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/huong-dan-cai-dat-AMP-cho-blog-WordPress-mien-phi-768x384.png",768,384,true],"large":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/huong-dan-cai-dat-AMP-cho-blog-WordPress-mien-phi.png",1024,512,false],"1536x1536":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/huong-dan-cai-dat-AMP-cho-blog-WordPress-mien-phi.png",1024,512,false],"2048x2048":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/huong-dan-cai-dat-AMP-cho-blog-WordPress-mien-phi.png",1024,512,false],"pk-small":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/huong-dan-cai-dat-AMP-cho-blog-WordPress-mien-phi.png",80,40,false],"pk-thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/huong-dan-cai-dat-AMP-cho-blog-WordPress-mien-phi.png",300,150,false]},"post_excerpt_stackable":"<p>Google AMP l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u